The paper deals with handwriting recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves training a deep neural network, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The READ dataset used in the experiments is a collection of historical documents, which could also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
